Since the upgrade to V0.7.1 compared to V 0.6 the realised estimand expressions for my DAGs have changed, leading to different estimates for the causal effects.

For example, given the simple DAG for the treatment T and the response variable R, and two other nodes A and B
digraph {
A;
B;   
T;
R;
A -> B; A -> R;
B -> T;
T -> R;
}

With dowhy V0.6 the realized estimand = T + B +A
but 
with dowhy V0.7.1 the realized estimand = T + A

Why has this behaviour changed? Is the newer version more accurate?
